00f30d361a9","tid":1735964,"uid":145423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:44:42.000Z","msg":"但所以佢依家咪著手拉出面救人果D囉, 出面就黎拉得多過入面架啦, 出面當場被拉入硬, 你明唔明呀, 入面都起碼可以打官司, 狗舉證難"},{"pid":"9bc3877c8c2b5d41c3f11b920578a8ed2b770ec4","tid":1735964,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:46:01.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n對面底牌好重要"},{"pid":"71c8967f2fb939e4bed4fc58289201d56d8ca330","tid":1735964,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:46:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4ef46eb061fe11531ed2222809317f19b71190","tid":1735964,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:49:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8995520dd7ed07c82c8ed14a415e274e103d7bbd","tid":1735964,"uid":336769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【唔好自己出黎，留守扮受害者最好】</span></span><br />\n雖然知PolyU夠勇，但<span style=\"color: red;\">popo明顯係唔想攻入去</span>，因為一攻入去就會輸哂國際線，加上法律上唔夠料告得入，佢只想你自己出黎，<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講&quot;投降&quot;/ &quot;自首&quot;</span></span></span>，千祈唔好中佢地計，已經好多人中左計被捕。<br />\n<br />\n留番係PolyU，有必要可以落Gear [反正唔應該再衝]。你地要扮 Victim，到時真係被人餓死左，國際線好易打。<span style=\"color: red;\">被捕時一定要Press影住</span>。街坊唔好講明去增援/開缺口，反而用<span style=\"color: red;\">人道理由</span>要求開路，運送食物+FA，要國際傳媒影住，popo唔俾，就加強我地國際線。<br />\n<br />\n既然<span style=\"color: red;\">命得一條，就要好好善用</span>，人地重狗，我地唔可以跌入圏套行出去，唔好跟佢地劇本。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全港諗緊計，Stay Strong</span><br />\n<br />\n永遠支持PolyU!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">Btw, 留意假記者/FA/政客/社工。</span>"},{"pid":"d531e8de9fb60804ade07aabbe66141d912cf614","tid":1735964,"uid":181531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075dc4b0912c50826add6e53d0b0025913181cb9","tid":1735964,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:53:35.000Z","msg":"班曱甴一向鍾意show off power<br />\n攻得入唔會唔攻"},{"pid":"a078e0dacf2691803407b659cf5a1d20b9063341","tid":1735964,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:53:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1607fd19b6fe71cace8d1a7aee8550451704fa90","tid":1735964,"uid":181531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:54:14.000Z","msg":"打咗個冇價值嘅陣地<br />\n幾百手足為救被捕<br />\n你依家嚟投降<br />\n我真係屌你老母呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92218048f02b4b57e5c7dd48de0d419d61581467","tid":1735964,"uid":61603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:54:23.000Z","msg":"唔好出黎呀屌 尖東搵生命推緊入黎 拉既拉傷既傷<br />\n<br />\n就算出！！！<br />\n【請廣傳予身處理大人士】<br />\n<br />\n許智峯呼籲，無論你離開的方式如何，在任何情況下，請勿向任何人表達你「投降」或「自首」，因這樣有可能影響你日後的法律權利，緊記！<br />\n<br />\n另外，整塊牌，寫住 [被困理大，非示威者]，傳媒直播下手拖手行出黎，到時狗只可以拘捕，唔打得被困市民，告暴動就一定，不過無乜可能告得入<br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"f4afc6a40efa40888635ae0d2476f94b7557b278","tid":1735964,"uid":209177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19d29b8cdd52c1f82e898467eb0f71e07c7478d7","tid":1735964,"uid":181531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"075dc4b0912c50826add6e53d0b0025913181cb9","tid":1735964,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:53:35.000Z","msg":"班曱甴一向鍾意show off power<br />\n攻得入唔會唔攻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:55:56.000Z","msg":"要攻一早就入咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明顯有政治考慮"}]}